title: Hallmark-In My Dreams [2014]
description:
Hallmark-In My Dreams (2014) 

Air Date: 20 Apr 2014

Summary: Natalie and Nick are frustrated with their luck in romance. After tossing coins into a fountain, the two then begin dreaming about each other. But, according to fountain mythology, they only have a week to turn those dreams into reality.
